NAME implementer

INPUT task
  API specification to implement

GOAL implement -> server_code
  Implement the API in Go using net/http (no frameworks).
  Include:
  - Router setup with middleware chain
  - Handler functions (one per endpoint)
  - Request validation
  - Error response helpers
  - Graceful shutdown
  
  No database — use in-memory store with sync.RWMutex.
  Output ONLY the code.
